      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber. This example has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, maintaining a showroom-quality presentation that defies its tenure. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. For the discerning collector or executive seeking uncompromising excellence, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
