    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly breathtaking condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a flawless finish with no swirls, chips, or imperfections, while the interior retains that fresh, new-car scent with supple, unmarked leather and pristine trim throughout. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete paper trail included for your peace of mind. From the crystal-clear headlights to the spotless engine bay and curb-rash-free alloys, this car has been meticulously garaged and pampered. It is a turn-key collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
