    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total gem! This beauty is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've pampered this car since day one, always keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream! I'm really going to miss it, but I\u2019m excited for it to go to a home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
