    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade specimen of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2-liter naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system, providing a visceral power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile shifts, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures precise power delivery. This vehicle has undergone extensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe. The chassis remains taut with fresh bushings and factory-spec suspension geometry, preserving the iconic 50/50 weight distribution. With zero oxidation and pristine paint depth, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
